---
title: Roasted Dill-Garlic Salmon with Warm Orzo and Spinach Salad
description: This Greek-inspired pasta salad comes together in no time with the help of creamy tzatziki, and it serves as the perfect side for simple dill-garlic salmon. A touch of olives and feta confirms that tonight's dinner is fit for Grecian gods!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-roti-a-laneth-et-a-lail-7b2dbb3b.jpg
